message.content:
Changes committed and pushed. Summary of what was done:

Fixed floating panel issues:

- Window resizing now works and remembers size/position using `electron-window-state` (persisted in OS config)
- Native drag region implemented with `-webkit-app-region: drag` CSS property (no JS drag logic, eliminates flicker)
- Window enabled as resizable with min 280×200 constraints
- EIO console logging crash fixed with fallback to file logging
- `electron-window-state` externalized in build to avoid bundling errors
- Reduced excessive logging on window move and message flush

Other fixes:

- `node scripts/start-headful.mjs --profile weibo_fresh --url https://weibo.com` now launches headful (with browser) correctly (headless is optional boolean flag, defaults to false)
- Console health check logging consolidated to reduce noise

Temporary files excluded from commit:

- `.bak`, `.bak2`, build artifacts (`*.js`, `*.mjs`), and diag.ts remain untracked and not pushed

To test: `node scripts/start-headful.mjs --profile weibo_fresh --url https://weibo.com`
